{"tid":1918443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵花3億元翻新太子警察會所 被揭計入沙中線工程開支","createTime":"2020-03-10T06:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T08:56:57.000Z","uid":154787,"like":69,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"5405f161e1057fee7f3a6de5b163e66e2a419b0e","tid":1918443,"uid":154787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣避風塘附近的警官會所受沙中線工程影響而被拆卸，但港鐵除負責事後原址重建該會所外，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>另耗資近3億港元公帑翻新與沙中線走線無關、位於太子的警察體育遊樂會會所，該筆款項計入沙中線總工程開支，即以公帑支付</strong></span></span>，事件亦引起外界關注。運輸及房屋局今(5日)回應立法會提問，指3億港元費用中，絕大部分為結構及機電工程費用，購買家具及設備費用只佔其中少於1%。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">日經都要講句，搭黨鐵原來係幫黑警會所埋單，香港人就比佢哋又拉又打，你地仲搭唔搭</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d62c6abc81255c0dcee108b8ed4597e7e37eee","tid":1918443,"uid":231571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:12:44.000Z","msg":"推 之前都有講過<br />\n唔好放過佢"},{"pid":"620ea2932bb8e073ce1f7df8fbca405dbfb71482","tid":1918443,"uid":51294,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:14:07.000Z","msg":"記低邊個負責，普選後 要送呢班人坐監"},{"pid":"31ab866f3e9dda9ce7dc4a702406b5678a88d7a0","tid":1918443,"uid":2008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:15:04.000Z","msg":"1%都已經300萬啦"},{"pid":"278e4fe939a18af14af8e087d751cc9f7180b5b5","tid":1918443,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54945ddc13dd56629a43b5cb0bbdf9e57d8636a9","tid":1918443,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:16:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6940b6e4b729c02770575df686822407de8fa2f9","tid":1918443,"uid":230104,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"消失的ICAC"},{"pid":"75b2dd03ea577ffccbae3048eb257864c114253f","tid":1918443,"u